1c1cb14d6d50d25553004499a3e9d418803d0bf8.query:
SELECT
					a.name as a,
					b.name as b
				FROM names as a
					CROSS JOIN names as b
				WHERE
					(a.name, b.name) > ($1, $2)
				ORDER BY a.name, b.name
				LIMIT $3

3ff0d660ab6aac497a6a391a8c317dd2ef3d5aaa.query:
SELECT
			count(*) as "count!"
		FROM names
		WHERE
			CASE $1
				WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
				WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
				WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
			END

8465250b59cbb5caa0ad63a8fea0a3446520553a.query:
SELECT
			count(*)
		FROM similarities
		INNER JOIN names ON
			b = name
		WHERE
			(a = $1)
			AND (a != b)
			AND
				CASE $2
					WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
					WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
					WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
				END
			AND (levenshtein < $3)

8888067d3205499f00ce1669c7d7de3bd88826fb.query:
SELECT
			name as "name!",
			gender as "gender!: Gender"
		FROM names
		WHERE
			CASE $1
				WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
				WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
				WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
			END
		ORDER BY RANDOM()
		LIMIT 1

			source
		) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
		ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING

8abbf2bed3048b8040d51ba5234c55486e9a34b8.query:
INSERT INTO names (
			name,
			gender
		) VALUES ($1, $2)
		ON CONFLICT DO
		UPDATE
		SET
			gender = CASE names.gender
				WHEN 'female' THEN
					CASE $2
						WHEN 'female' THEN 'female'
						ELSE 'both'
					END
				WHEN 'male' THEN
					CASE $2
						WHEN 'male' THEN 'male'
						ELSE 'both'
					END
				WHEN 'both' THEN 'both'
			END

9ffd255654d4d9c68771007980feac05fc23db90.query:
SELECT
			name as "name!",
			gender as "gender!: Gender"
		FROM names
		WHERE
			CASE $1
				WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
				WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
				WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
			END
		ORDER BY name ASC
		LIMIT 1
		OFFSET $2

c5ab1af80960aacbbc89f69043eb2ed8898bdee4.query:
SELECT
			name as "name!",
			gender as "gender!: Gender"
		FROM similarities
		INNER JOIN names ON
			b = name
		WHERE
			(a = $1)
			AND (a != b)
			AND
				CASE $2
					WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
					WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
					WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
				END
			AND (levenshtein < $3)
		ORDER BY b DESC
		LIMIT -1
		OFFSET $4

ed1d76caa95d45cad60ff1c2e26549f0f3cf863e.query:
INSERT INTO similarities (
			a,
			b,
			levenshtein,
			longest_common_substring,
			longest_common_substring_similarity
		) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
		ON CONFLICT DO
		UPDATE
		SET
			levenshtein = $3,
			longest_common_substring = $4,
			longest_common_substring_similarity = $5

f0602d903e4539ccacd42266dc276f30efed3288.query:
SELECT
				name,
				gender as "gender: Gender"
			FROM names
			WHERE
				name > $1
				AND CASE $2
					WHEN 'both' THEN TRUE
					WHEN 'female' THEN gender != 'male'
					WHEN 'male' THEN gender != 'female'
				END
			ORDER BY name ASC
			LIMIT $3
